HEADWORD: Kish
<hw>Kish</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. G. <ets>kies</ets>
gravel, pyrites.]</ety> <fld>(Min.)</fld> <def>A workman's name for the
